title: Dating Your Manager, Freezing Your Eggs & Becoming A Cougar ft. Rosanna Pansino
description:
Baking sensation Rosanna Pansino joins Wild 'Til 9 to recount her highest and lowest moments of "making it" in LA and what it's like to date your manager of 10+ years. She shares her experience on the process of freezing your eggs and navigating life with dyslexia.
